	      <LI><P>Fetch the <a href=./file/Xrcc1.fasta>sequence</a>.</P></LI>
	      <LI><P>Make a Blast against SwissProt to try to find homologues.</P></LI>
	      <LI><P>Compare the remote homologues you may find using dottlet or dotter.</P></LI> 
	      <LI><P>Make a multiple alignment of the homologous segments you found.</P></LI> 
	      <LI><P>Make a psi-blast using any of the segments.</P></LI> 
	      <LI><P>make a multiple alignment to convince yourself of the similarity with the DNA ligase.</P></LI> 
